{"tid":705149,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一日n個地理冷知識","createTime":"2018-06-17T01:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T11:54:44.000Z","uid":140953,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"79c9d8f1b5afecfaf34f62ed12f3fd034242f8a9","tid":705149,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T01:44:54.000Z","msg":"我講下城市溫度<br />\n冰島唔係真係咁凍<br />\n雖然首都夏天平均都只係10幾度<br />\n但冬天反而都只係0度上下<br />\n以最凍既一月份為例<br />\n冰島首都平均最高及最低溫係3.3/-2.3度<br />\n反而鄰近既首爾係1.6/-6.1度<br />\n原因係冰島附近既氣流調節左溫度，令到冰島雖然好北，但可以保持更細既溫差同更高既溫度<br />\n所以有時候聽人講冬天去冰島以為好勁，其實仲暖過你去首爾同東京<br />\n<br />\n其次係非洲<br />\n非洲有好多唔同既國家，唔係個個都好熱<br />\n好似肯亞首都，海拔1600米<br />\n所以雖然係赤道，但平均最高氣溫反而只係25度，平均最低氣溫更只有12度<br />\n更唔好講唔少遠離赤道既非洲國家一樣有買季同埋有冬天<br />\n所以非洲人係香港想返自己國家避暑唔係冇可能"},{"pid":"c0681ad789d2deb7c845fb01c16279258deae433","tid":705149,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T01:56:08.000Z","msg":"高質post"},{"pid":"a06d4a9ba3c8cba85fe7c3b1934cdbb05b8a0570","tid":705149,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T01:58:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e594efc4ba263318cb63fa23382dd3c76f0d6c","tid":705149,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:01:19.000Z","msg":"陸地仲有好多未俾人發掘到 係咪真"},{"pid":"806ff3e3b7d40cb85c6b079fc774884125048bc9","tid":705149,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:20:00.000Z","msg":"冰島有個冰字令人覺得凍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8faec624a59cf02d05f620570402ad19d311b9f5","tid":705149,"uid":179547,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/17/102618_00e1c7a8536a4f2644d8a172f79b9e21.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F102618_00e1c7a8536a4f2644d8a172f79b9e21.png&h=d8c863bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f840812eef063175eace81b47e8d79ac4e8f92c","tid":705149,"uid":11261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:26:43.000Z","msg":"我都鍾意研究地理<br />\n有fd去旅行，但地理、歷史知識係零，我覺得冇咗去旅行嘅意義"},{"pid":"0891727d9f03d7c72f3a04c95fd3c8f8e0e48594","tid":705149,"uid":53589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T11:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/de/Karte_Karibik_Inseln_%28zh%29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fd%2Fde%2FKarte_Karibik_Inseln_%2528zh%2529.png&h=33ba35c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西印度群島唔係印度洋, 而係中美洲加勒比海, 個名係因為當年哥倫布以為自己到左印度"}]}